    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Trade name for small semi-antique west Anatolian rugs, often with a light ground and distinctive elaborate double-niche design.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
